collections.name: Nariscia's Magical Portals: The Continuum
collections.description:
Nariscia's Magical Portals: The Continuum opens the door to a new world of discovery. This collection blends simplicity with complexity, offering a diverse range of portals that cater to different energies and experiences. While some portals feature calming aura colours designed to soothe and ground, others are more intricate, offering deeper layers of complexity for those who seek a more intense journey.

The Continuum is about balance and exploration. It invites you to experience a new magical world with its own unique vibrational frequencies, each portal offering a distinct way to meditate, heal, and connect.

Each portal is infused with binary code and powerful affirmations, guiding you on your personal journey of self-love and self-expansion.

As a special gift, for every three portals collected, you will gain access to an exclusive guided meditation to deepen your journey and enhance your experience.

collections.name: Neon Pikachu
collections.description:
In a world increasingly embracing digital art and collectibles, we introduce the Neon Pikachu NFT Collection, combining the iconic Pikachu with futuristic neon aesthetics. This unique collection blends entertainment and technology, creating exclusive digital collectibles that will captivate Pokémon fans and enthusiasts of NFT art.

The Neon Pikachu NFT Collection offers exclusive, one-of-a-kind digital artworks designed to showcase modern technology and creativity. Each NFT in the collection is unique, making it ideal for collectors seeking to own something that is not just digital art, but also a symbol of the future of collecting.

Join the revolution in the world of digital art and become part of a community leading the NFT revolution. The Neon Pikachu NFT Collection is just the beginning of your journey through a world that will surprise you with its creativity and innovations.

This extraordinary collection features 29 unique NFT pages, each a one-of-a-kind work of art. Each page serves as a key to the mysteries of summoning incarnate gods and spirits, unlocking ancient magic inaccessible to ordinary mortals. The unique symbols on each page act as magical seals, each associated with one of the names of Nyarlathotep.

collections.name: Burn Wishlist Vol. 1
collections.description:
A curated gallery of digital oopsies, public missteps, awkward artifacts, and inconvenient truths — all legally obtained, publicly available, and now permanently preserved on-chain.

These are the things powerful people would love to scrub from the internet:

- That photo op gone wrong
- The press release they "revised"
- The tweet they deleted
- The document that somehow made it out
- And yes, that unflattering portrait they’ve been trying to make disappear

Each NFT is a tasteful little monument to their discomfort — a reminder that in a decentralized world, you can’t unmint the truth.

They wish it never existed.
We made it collectible.

**Let’s see how much they’re willing to pay to burn it from the chain.**
